sequenceDiagram
    participant S as Your Machine
    participant R1 as Router 1
    participant R2 as Router 2
    participant R3 as Router 3
    participant D as Destination

    Note over S: TTL = 1
    S->>R1: UDP packet (TTL=1)
    R1-->>S: ICMP Time Exceeded (Type 11)
    Note over S: Got Router 1's IP ✓

    Note over S: TTL = 2
    S->>R1: UDP packet (TTL=2)
    R1->>R2: TTL decremented to 1
    R2-->>S: ICMP Time Exceeded (Type 11)
    Note over S: Got Router 2's IP ✓

    Note over S: TTL = 3
    S->>R1: UDP packet (TTL=3)
    R1->>R2: TTL decremented to 2
    R2->>R3: TTL decremented to 1
    R3-->>S: ICMP Time Exceeded (Type 11)
    Note over S: Got Router 3's IP ✓

    Note over S: TTL = 4
    S->>R1: UDP packet (TTL=4)
    R1->>R2: TTL decremented to 3
    R2->>R3: TTL decremented to 2
    R3->>D: TTL decremented to 1
    D-->>S: ICMP Port Unreachable (Type 3)
    Note over S: Reached destination ✓
